Generic single-database configuration with async support.

This is an Alembic migration configuration for our RAG chatbot application.
It supports async database operations and uses SQLAlchemy 2.0 style models.

To create a new migration:
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

To upgrade to the latest version:
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

To downgrade one version:
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

To get current version:
```bash
alembic current
```

To get migration history:
```bash
alembic history
```
